      <title>瑞银财富管理将美联储降息预期推迟至六月</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/ubs-wealth-management-pushes-back-fed-rate-cut-forecast-june-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银全球财富管理表示，目前预计美联储将于 6 月开始降息，而此前的预期是从 5 月开始降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/ubs-wealth-management-pushes-back-fed-rate-cut-forecast-june-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 09:44:54 GMT</pubDate>
