    <item>
      <title>红海弹道导弹袭击引发亚洲对防御的兴趣</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/red-sea-ballistic-missile-attacks-trigger-asian-interest-defences-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[专家和行业官员表示，在红海使用反舰弹道导弹（ASBM）激发了亚洲对用于击落反舰弹道导弹的系统的兴趣，尽管中国拥有庞大的反舰弹道导弹武库，构成了更严峻的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/red-sea-ballistic-missile-attacks-trigger-asian-interest-defences-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 09:39:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TotalEnergies 与空中客车公司签署可持续航空燃料合作伙伴关系</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/totalenergies-airbus-sign-partnership-sustainable-aviation-fuel-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国能源集团周三表示，TotalEnergies 已与空中客车公司签署战略合作伙伴关系，根据该合作伙伴关系，TotalEnergies 将为这家飞机制造商提供可持续航空燃料，以满足其在欧洲一半以上的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/totalenergies-airbus-sign-partnership-sustainable-aviation-fuel-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 09:31:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本因消费支出低迷而下调经济前景</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japan-downgrades-view-economy-sluggish-consumer-spending-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费者支出低迷，日本政府在二月份三个月来首次下调了对经济的看法，这表明在工资复苏缓慢和工业产出低迷的情况下走出衰退的道路崎岖不平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japan-downgrades-view-economy-sluggish-consumer-spending-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 09:25:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
