      <title>支持战争的俄罗斯商人将接管达能的俄罗斯资产 - FT</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/danone-planning-sell-russian-operations-chechnya-linked-businessman-ft-report-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据英国《金融时报》周三报道，在莫斯科暂时控制几个月后，一名在 Instagram 上标榜自己支持战争的俄罗斯商人正计划以 177 亿卢布（1.9152 亿美元）收购达能的俄罗斯资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/danone-planning-sell-russian-operations-chechnya-linked-businessman-ft-report-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 06:32:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
