      <title>最终，“错失恐惧症”(FOMO) 将日本股市重新列入全球愿望清单</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/last-fomo-puts-japans-stocks-back-global-wishlist-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日经指数攀升至历史新高，标志着日本股市长期走出投资荒野，日本企业的资金、势头和变化迹象使市场重新回到全球投资组合的首位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/last-fomo-puts-japans-stocks-back-global-wishlist-2024-02-21/</guid>
